{{Top|leg}}
'''Lowickese''' was the native language of the [[Pa'lowick/Legends|Pa'lowick]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Lowick/Legends|Lowick]]. Most Pa'lowicks were fluent in both Lowickese and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]].

Lowickese originally had no written form. However, with the introduction of Lowick to the [[The galaxy/Legends|galactic]] community, Pa'lowicks had adapted Basic alphabet to create a written form of Lowickese. To the laypeople, it looked like nonsense written in Basic. Ironically, Pa'lowicks usually were literate in Lowickese, but not in Basic.

